## Files to create
- `backend/src/test/java/com/shiftworks/jobops/service/BackupServiceTest.java`

## Context

`BackupService` uses `mysqldump` / `mysql` subprocesses and AES-GCM encryption. Since subprocess calls are hard to mock, we focus on testing the `listBackups()` method and the `restore()` validation logic (rejects non-COMPLETED backups). The `performBackup` subprocess path is best covered by integration tests, so here we test the guard rails.

