## Priority: LOW â€” Backup/restore is security-critical but execution path is untested

## Files to modify
- `backend/src/test/java/com/shiftworks/jobops/service/BackupServiceTest.java`

## Instructions

Open `backend/src/test/java/com/shiftworks/jobops/service/BackupServiceTest.java`.

Add these imports at the top (after existing imports):

```java
import com.shiftworks.jobops.config.AppProperties;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Path;
```

Add the following test method inside the `BackupServiceTest` class:

```java
    @Test
    void performBackupCreatesRecordWithCorrectFields() {
        AppProperties.Storage storage = new AppProperties.Storage();
        storage.setBackupPath(System.getProperty("java.io.tmpdir") + "/shiftworks-test-backups");
